    "patch_code": "private static final int MAX_DEPTH = 256;\nprivate boolean inSpecificScope(String[] targetNames, String[] baseTypes, String[] extraTypes) {\n    // https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/parsing.html#has-an-element-in-the-specific-scope\n    int depth = stack.size()-1;\n    if (depth > MAX_DEPTH){\n        throw new RuntimeException(\"Reach max scope search depth:\" + MAX_DEPTH);\n    }\n    \n    for (int i = depth; i >= 0; --i){\n        final String elName = stack.get(i).nodeName();\n        \n        if (isInArray(elName,targetNames)){\n            return true;\n        }\n        if (isInArray(elName,baseTypes)){\n            return false;\n        }\n        if ((extraTypes != null) && isInArray(elName,extraTypes)){\n            return false;\n        }\n    }\n    return false;\n}\npublic static boolean isInArray(String val,String[] arr){\n    for(String s:arr){\n        if(val.equalsIgnoreCase(s)){\n            return true;\n        }\n    }\n    return false;\n}",
